data.value:
With 80 players slots, this is the main roleplay server for LimeLight Gaming. Go out of town, or stay within the city with great RP opportunities for you to use!
Tip: New to Rockford? Use /map in-game to help you get around!

data.name: metroLabel3.Text
data.value:
With 25 player slots, this server is dedicated to the members wanting to let their imagination go wild with creations to support your RP!
With multiple features to help you build, such as noclip, and the quietness to help you concentrate.

data.name: metroLabel6.Text
data.value:
Hello and welcome to my LimeLight Gaming unofficial launcher. This tool was mainly created due to myself having an interest in coding C# and VB.net, and not knowing what to create. Yeah, then it was pretty much me remembering my tutorial for creating an easy shortcut to load right into the server, I thought to myself, "huh, would be cool if I could create a cool interface for loading into the Limelight servers".
Well yeah, that's pretty much how this got created, but anyway, more about this tool, it was created in C# and uses JSON.net for an upcoming updates feature which utilises the Limelight Gaming Update API to show a few of the latest updates on the "Welcome" screen, MetroFramework is also used for the cool metro style design. I had fun creating this tool, I actually have fun making anything in Visual Studio, because I can extend my learning in coding.
Anyway, I hope this tool becomes somewhat useful for people!
